{"tid":1801622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港反滲透第一課：認識紅色滲透的原理","createTime":"2019-12-28T18:44:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T19:04:28.000Z","uid":7736,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4059d8b9fb7c02ecb1fad2c3e9ed6039a42e27aa","tid":1801622,"uid":7736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T18:44:53.000Z","msg":"先了解共產黨員點樣滲透，來反滲透<br />\n<br />\n共產黨員滲透分四大類。<br />\n<br />\n第一層 黑線<br />\n隱藏得好深嘅共產黨員<br />\n<br />\n第二層 灰線<br />\n或明或暗的黨員，你完全唔知佢的背景<br />\n<br />\n第三層 粉紅線<br />\n表面上親共，但佢絕對不會當面承認<br />\n<br />\n第四層 紅線<br />\n公開的共產黨員<br />\n<br />\n其餘大家睇片學野。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/BlPwFgoSJww\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBlPwFgoSJww&d=9uLtkTaOKuy%2FgkD%2BHbzoNbccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=2615c109\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/BlPwFgoSJww</a><br />\n<br />\n同場加影分析，共產黨最終目的。<br />\n小國家的生存之道，<br />\n華人民族主義，如何被共產黨利用的運作。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/fSRuUssIRGU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FfSRuUssIRGU&d=9uLtkTaOKuy%2FgkD%2BHbzoNbccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=e2c44691\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fSRuUssIRGU</a>"},{"pid":"eee3205641fec9819553a1dc4b12ea76317be354","tid":1801622,"uid":284463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T18:48:59.000Z","msg":"黃色經濟圈的障礙<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1801188\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1801188</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cde2eb80df8ca2f8e71d0604ccd77424e1cf856b","tid":1801622,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T19:00:19.000Z","msg":"明居正「透視中國」：中共如何控制香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1565658/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1565658/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"88f8ff2c3a4f3e43a4ef2d25ebcf17c7a49a1773","tid":1801622,"uid":336764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T19:03:18.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"60f457bc2aac67ca3cfe88f1da0b5a4b4b5e3cbf"